What:		/sys/class/power_supply/<supply_name>/voltage_now,
Date:		May 2007
Contact:	linux-pm@vger.kernel.org
Description:
		Battery:

		  Reports an instant, single VBAT voltage reading for the
		  battery. This value is not averaged/smoothed.

		  Access: Read

